<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">Good morning, <o:p></o:p></span=
></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">We have spoken to the client an=
d the have advised the third party hit them at such force that the TP vehic=
le went down the side of his vehicle after the first point of contact and h=
e advised that all 3 damages were caused
 by the third party. <o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">The third-party insurers have a=
dmitted liability but have not received an engineer report from us.
<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">We will proceed with caution an=
d wait for the third-party insurers to review our engineer report before ge=
tting the vehicle into the garage.
<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">Kind regards<o:p></o:p></span><=
/p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">Sophie <o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
